{"tid":2005171,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"懲教一哥胡英明係2019年2月頭已部署好酷刑迫害政治犯","createTime":"2020-05-07T02:40:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-02T05:37:05.000Z","uid":26770,"like":62,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"28ede5a34f6e80eb5c0f06dcfb6011cab7ad0f7c","tid":2005171,"uid":26770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T02:40:14.000Z","msg":"知唔知點解斷正左胡英明都唔交人<br />\n<br />\n睇左先<br />\n<br />\n懲教署推「智慧監獄」 引入手帶新閉路電視防自殺| <a href=\"http://頭條日報hd.stheadline.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E9%A0%AD%E6%A2%9D%E6%97%A5%E5%A0%B1hd.stheadline.com&d=w9JnFmhD9tlFtzSpwKDBdR6eP3a%2FjAUraAi1lUB%2B7iI%3D&h=20b60c72\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E9%A0%AD%E6%A2%9D%E6%97%A5%E5%A0%B1hd.stheadline.com&h=e59e27c5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">頭條日報hd.stheadline.com</a> &rsaquo; news &rsaquo; <br />\nFeb 14, 2019 - 懲教署署長胡英明強調「電腦不會百分百取代人類，機械人只是協助。」 羅湖懲教所將試行「維生指標監察系統」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">唔單係指使獄卒打政治犯<br />\n2019年已引入監控手環防止受害人自殺<br />\n<ins>監控到你自殺就拉走再暴打<br />\n</ins><br />\n慘撚過無間地獄, 大家明因何前線手足認罪未<br />\n香港懲教根本係香港警魔係反人類大道上的恩師<br />\n<br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"0f459c570f016493ea21483516d6e675840666b5","tid":2005171,"uid":280648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T02:44:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"928a1cf25016e034f472db717a6f5598f29106f4","tid":2005171,"uid":26770,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T02:44:14.000Z","msg":"懲教一哥胡英明對付後生咪就係用<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">中共對維吾爾人果套</span><br />\n<br />\n就係不停折磨你,要異見人士生不如死<br />\n重點係呢班反人類惡魔唔會比警暴受害人輕易死亡<br />\n<br />\n同香港警魔係新屋嶺輪姦婦女係同一種手法"},{"pid":"8ae0b74cfe38604b741eac83d4f8e19657cc03d9","tid":2005171,"uid":26770,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T02:54:05.000Z","msg":"香港人的境況已等於維族人<br />\n懲教胡英明等人就係納粹軍頭<br />\n<br />\n根本未開始反修例中共就已部署好滅殺香港人<br />\n可見就算香港人當時無選擇反抗, 其實中共一樣會預防性屠殺香港人"},{"pid":"f03368611629d809c425933235b509680df0f01e","tid":2005171,"uid":181549,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T02:59:01.000Z","msg":"做香港人真係好撚慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"096965dbe42e35fe7781b77e69ef5636ddec4177","tid":2005171,"uid":92385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T03:00:07.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"420882ae2f8fd33440da1b39e6fc85299af7691e","tid":2005171,"uid":64056,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T03:00:54.000Z","msg":"跑步單野點<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6190d1ad44b6e9b5f5e9a609adf2d7ced2e4c1e0","tid":2005171,"uid":26770,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"f03368611629d809c425933235b509680df0f01e","tid":2005171,"uid":181549,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T02:59:01.000Z","msg":"做香港人真係好撚慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T03:02:02.000Z","msg":"其實香港人睇漏唔少惡魔<br />\n懲教一哥胡英明<br />\n刑事檢控專員梁卓然<br />\n統籌各大商場安閉路以協助捉女示威者淫樂的輔警總監新地高層「槍王」楊祖賜"},{"pid":"477114b21522eac4b66412493bd9f2fec892064b","tid":2005171,"uid":94069,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T03:03:46.000Z","msg":"香港=新疆"},{"pid":"e5b7dd8eaf612573c357ae484e801ba6be9cffb3","tid":2005171,"uid":26770,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T03:08:44.000Z","msg":"胡英明同梁卓然係同一類人<br />\n惡毒陰狠但城府深, 低調地做實事反人類<br />\n<br />\n而鄉黑強好回味做暗星日子<br />\n所以做完壞事急住去區議會做表演<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">但雖然性格唔同,反人類本質係無分別</span>"},{"pid":"9df216ba51cca816bb91305685a79466da0902f1","tid":2005171,"uid":26770,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T03:13:39.000Z","msg":"我平時一開post一大班pprb五毛狂攪我<br />\n大把會員可以做我的證人<br />\n<br />\n我屌胡英明你班撚屌唔還手護住<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">懲教一哥胡英明起碼都係香港狗方係酷刑一事的授孽恩師</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n走狗果然天生反骨"},{"pid":"3bd4cb49ab1c23414af3d059d538cf8aa3867c83","tid":2005171,"uid":229920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T03:17:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2090bc3fc63cae8291f91700e53e2a33a84d4d04","tid":2005171,"uid":15644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T03:20:01.000Z","msg":"Agger"},{"pid":"eb09dcdf7d3c14f03e6659b08727af60706dff96","tid":2005171,"uid":128763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T03:20:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"20040e469e94e649d16a8757a084ed1dce937df6","tid":2005171,"uid":237425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T03:21:54.000Z","msg":"巴士底監獄"},{"pid":"382c5f077e43482e2bae216b2063b3c69bb25ab2","tid":2005171,"uid":26770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T03:27:39.000Z","msg":"1淫賤穴蛾借疫情推監控手環<br />\n2 doj刑事檢控專員梁卓然濫告後生仔, 香港黨委法官扮好人話咩引入監控手環就比保釋<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">點解所有高層都spin去香港全民要用監控手環</span><br />\n<br />\n無香港記者敢講敢問"},{"pid":"89282e86f9c42d8e4faefdf944e3b7d62bf0877e","tid":2005171,"uid":224657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T03:28:15.000Z","msg":"up"},{"pid":"b72e450393d49038fce84475714c70896cd29f32","tid":2005171,"uid":57542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T03:28:53.000Z","msg":"不安"},{"pid":"eada6128f842aeaed64713dfb4ddb449a4faeb2c","tid":2005171,"uid":8075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T04:22:11.000Z","msg":"diu up"},{"pid":"d96dfd335cca9d654352e3185ce2713b3ef1fd8b","tid":2005171,"uid":26770,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0